{"tid":628521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯駐美使館警告美英法空襲行動不會沒後果","createTime":"2018-04-14T03:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T20:36:57.000Z","uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"bcaa545370dae6be18a4119d0abc7b8b747088f9","tid":628521,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:03:49.000Z","msg":"美國聯同英法兩國攻擊敘利亞的軍事及化武設施。俄羅斯駐美大使館表示，美國與盟友的行動是對俄羅斯總統普京的「侮辱」，做法不可接受，並警告空襲行動不會沒有後果，所有責任歸於美、英、法三方。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯國防委員會副主席亞歷山大謝林形容特朗普是「希特拉二號」，批評美軍的空襲行為違反國際法，亦是對俄羅斯的侵略。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391146-20180414.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391146-20180414.htm&d=a2fAEDvJX9cUVbNvmf2p58PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2b8673bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391146-20180414.htm&h=14ac1e84\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391146-20180414.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e426f2b288e8014783f8680b49a3bcea902c23d8","tid":628521,"uid":33481,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:04:42.000Z","msg":"顫抖民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa96bab6b80cd9f0aeae7f2ec3b4489b5fcf4c80","tid":628521,"uid":111965,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:05:01.000Z","msg":"哦國口交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99548fa246bab45b65ed74b655d644ba3fbd272c","tid":628521,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"還擊啦，講"},{"pid":"0bff88bf88bc4d459e6cd965fafffd362d78264b","tid":628521,"uid":2054,"like":12,